notes: Zimbabwe 50 runs in 72 mins 17.4 overs (Taibu 26*, Chigumbura 4*)
Zimbabwe 100 runs in 131 mins 30.4 overs (Taibu 68*, Maregwede 20*)
Zimbabwe 150 runs in 162 mins 41.2 overs (Taibu 73*, Maregwede 35*)
Zimbabwe 200 runs in 190 mins 49.2 overs (Taibu 94*, Nkala 24*)
Sri Lanka 50 runs in 52 mins 10.2 overs (Sangakkara 30*, Zoysa 2*)
KC Sangakkara 11th 50 in 73 minutes off 49 balls (6x4)
Rain interupts play at 14:17 local time, Sri Lanka 31/2 (6.5 ov)
Sri Lanka 100 runs in 92 mins 19.3 overs (Sangakkara 53*, Dilshan 14*)
Play resumed at 4pm local time, 33 overs, target 173
A Maregwede replaced T Taibu as wicket keeper in the 20th over
Sri Lanka won by 12 runs, target 133 off 27 overs
